rows.label: qst650303_msg0001
rows.name: I think we've found the head honcho.

rows.label: qst650303_msg0003
rows.name:
It looks a lot tougher than the
others we fought.

rows.label: qst650303_msg0004
rows.name:
Should the worst happen,
I'll draw her.

rows.label: qst650303_msg0008
rows.name:
She's too powerful for anyone
but a Blade to wield.

rows.label: qst650303_msg0009
rows.name:
I was hoping we'd be able to finish
this without unleashing her, but I guess
there's nothing else for it.

rows.label: qst650303_msg0010
rows.name:
Give me an opening and I'll
finish this with one blow.

rows.label: qst650303_msg0011
rows.name: We shall place our trust in you.

rows.label: qst650303_msg0013
rows.name: OK! Show us what you've got, Kamuya!
